<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>深夜，一辆监狱巴士等在美罗城监狱外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个狱警从监狱走出来看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很安全。把犯人带出来吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>又一个狱警出来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的身边站着一个带手铐的小丑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，  几个人影从黑暗中跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好！”第一个狱警大声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来了更多的小丑！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我今天真不想上学。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们一整天都会被关在教室里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和朋友们走在上学的路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉挠了挠头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 我以为今天魔术师会来学校呢！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他要给全校学生表演魔术。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你昨晚没收到潘校长的邮件吗？”特勒尔问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“魔术师感冒了。今天没有表演。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉皱起了眉头。“真可惜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望魔术师早点好起来。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说不定他能让所有老师都消失。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和特勒尔都笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉摇了摇头，叹了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许魔术师可以让你们俩消失。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉假装向杰克和特勒尔挥动魔术棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿布拉卡达布拉，变！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。“那会很有意思！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想看逃脱术。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“以前我在电视上看过一个男人逃脱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人被绑在很大的玻璃箱里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他必须在玻璃箱装满水以前逃脱！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克双臂交叉，假装挣扎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“说不定火箭女孩儿会来我们学校。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她会给我们展示她的各种超能力。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那将是最精彩的表演！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特勒尔为什么看我？”罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那会很酷！”玛拉突然说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西耸耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是会很酷。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我觉得火箭女孩儿不会来学校表演。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她停下来打开背包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……我带作业了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她一直等着朋友们走远了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔一直回头看她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长！”罗西小声说，“有什么事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207547</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有一个坏消息，火箭女孩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207547</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>市长看起来很严肃，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“昨天晚上一个危险的犯人从美罗城监狱逃走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁逃走了？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是我们市里最可怕、最邪恶的犯人之一。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长说。“他叫巴布斯。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西扬起一边的眉毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他叫巴布斯？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西耸耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道了，市长先生。我马上就到！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>